6. API REQUIREMENTS
==================================================
Implement these REST endpoints.

A. Register user
POST /api/users/register

Request:
- firstName
- lastName
- email
- phoneNumber
- password
- dateOfBirth
- city
- role(s) optional

Behavior:
- create user
- create profile
- assign default role RENTER if no roles provided
- password should be stored as passwordHash (simple placeholder hashing is acceptable, but structure code so BCrypt can be added later)

Response:
- created user profile data

B. Get user by id
GET /api/users/{userId}

C. Update basic profile
PUT /api/users/{userId}/profile

Request:
- firstName
- lastName
- phoneNumber
- city
- address
- profilePhotoUrl

D. Add/update driver license
PUT /api/users/{userId}/driver-license

Request:
- licenseNumber
- issuedDate
- expiryDate
- issuingCountry

E. Get renter validation profile for Rental Service
GET /api/users/{userId}/renter-profile

Response must include:
- renterId
- dateOfBirth
- driverLicenseExpiry
- drivingExperienceYears
- verifiedProfile
- homeCity

F. Get owner basic profile
GET /api/users/{userId}/owner-profile

Response:
- userId
- fullName
- phoneNumber
- city
- verifiedProfile

G. Verify user profile
PATCH /api/users/{userId}/verify

Behavior:
- set verifiedProfile = true
- optionally set status = ACTIVE if appropriate

H. Assign role
POST /api/users/{userId}/roles

Request:
{
  "role": "OWNER"
}

I. Get user roles
GET /api/users/{userId}/roles

