7. BUSINESS RULES
==================================================
Implement and document these rules:

1. Email must be unique
2. Password must not be blank during registration
3. User must be at least a reasonable minimum age (example: 18) to register
4. Driver license expiry must not be before issued date
5. Driving experience years should be calculated from license issued date, not manually entered
6. Verified profile is false by default
7. Default user status can be PENDING_VERIFICATION or ACTIVE, but document your choice clearly
8. A user can have multiple roles
9. Renter profile response must be optimized for Rental Service consumption
10. Owner profile response should expose only necessary public data

